  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Generate Staff Translation Keys from staff.yml Configuration\n\nFix the translation key generation process to properly extract and generate translation keys from the staff.yml configuration file.\n\nRequirements:\n- Investigate why staff.yml is not being processed by the translation key generator\n- Verify staff.yml file location, format, and syntax are correct\n- Ensure staff.yml is included in the translation generation pipeline\n- Check if other similar .yml files are being processed correctly and apply same logic\n- Validate that generated translation keys follow the expected naming convention\n- Test that generated keys are accessible and properly loaded in the application\n- Confirm all staff-related strings in staff.yml have corresponding translation keys created\n- Document the expected structure of staff.yml for translation generation\n\nEdge cases to consider:\n- Nested keys in staff.yml hierarchy\n- Missing or malformed YAML syntax\n- Translation key naming conflicts with existing keys\n- Locale-specific variations if multiple languages are supported",
